# Changelog

## [0.4.0] 2021-02-16

### Supervidor
 - Allow creating supervisor tasks to save 24/7 all radio stations

## [0.3.9] 2021-02-16

### File names
 - Allow to use a short name to improve chunk names

## [0.3.8] 2021-02-16

### Google Cloud storage
 - Allow to run it from command line

## [0.3.4] 2021-02-15

### Google Cloud storage
 - Added Google Cloud Storage Archiving feature
 - Allow reduce Audio as mono

## [0.3.3] 2021-02-14

### Command line tools added
 - `yaasr ls`
 - `yaasr test`
 - `yaasr info`
 - `yaasr record`

## [0.3.2] 2021-02-14

### Post processing audios
Allow post-process functions:

 - Allow to reformat audios (e.g. mp3 bitrate 16K)
 - Allow upload final audios using SSH
 - Allow delete previous version file after post-process

## [0.2.1] 2021-02-13

### Added
- Allow to save from external URL
